name: TiktaalikDreamings Realistic Weapon Pack
description:
Intended to add some vaguely more realistic weapons from history instead of the very fantasy cliche things in the game.  

A list of Items is here https://drive.google.com/file/d/1cTkd5ywF-1B9_VwyOHvri-QBNvMNvPp4/view?usp=sharing

Mod discord here https://discord.gg/XEUZxZRVF9
changeNote:
Remeshed Battlement using existing FunCom meshes and textures mixed with mine. 
Added a test focus for Set, no recipe, admin spawn only so far
Switched out most of my custom materials to instances of Funcom materials to have things like blood applied.
Removed a few unused assets that were auto-imported but not used.
